data.description: Immaculate 4 bedroom, 3-1 bath two story home situated on 5 beautiful acres with some woods. Numerous updates throughout & includes a finished lower level. The living room is open to the kitchen and allows a lot of natural light. The home also has a formal dining area, first floor study and a huge first floor laundry area! On the second floor, you will appreciate the size of the bedrooms and you will love the primary suite boasting a fireplace, whirlpool tub, shower & walk-in closet. Enjoy the privacy at the back of the home with large deck & above ground pool and 12x16 shed. The back acreage is perfect for a barn or outbuilding. Over 3,200 sq ft per Butler County. Convenient location just minutes  to Oxford or Hamilton. Geothermal heating system for low utility bills.
